      h3 Evan Coury (EvanDotPro)

      p Evan is a Zend certified engineer for PHP 5.3 and Zend Framework, as well as a regular speaker at developer conferences around the world. He's worked on and led many large-scale web development projects to success. When not in front of a computer, Evan enjoys being outdoors with his two border collies and doing anything related to aviation.

  .member.media
    .img: img src=gravatar("justin@roave.com")
    .content
      h3 Justin Martin (FrozenFire)

      p Justin Martin is a PHP expert with over a decade of highly diverse PHP experience. He is recognized in the PHP community for being <a href="significant contributor">a significant contributor</a> to the official PHP manual as well as a founding member of the <a href="http://phpmentoring.org/">PHP Mentoring</a> project. Justin is also our resident JavaScript and binary protocol expert.

      p Working independently for years, Justin has a wealth of experience in developing custom integrations for the <a href="https://www.mindbodyonline.com/">Mindbody Online</a> studio management system, building large-scale subscription-based video streaming solutions, and custom-flow ecommerce platforms. With Roave, Justin has focused on maintaining the <a href="http://smscloud.com/">SMSCloud</a> platform, as well as providing extensive support for <a href="http://www.callfire.com/">CallFire</a> as their resident PHP expert and custom solutions developer.

      p In his spare time, Justin enjoys riding motorcycles, bicycles, <a href="http://rvecafe.com/Assets5/bike01f.jpg">or anything with two wheels</a>.

